products.title: Naruto 2.0
products.author: Masashi Kishimoto
products.description: Naruto tells the story of Naruto Uzumaki, a young ninja with dreams of becoming the Hokage, the leader of his village. Despite being shunned due to the Nine-Tails Fox sealed inside him, Naruto pushes forward, forming bonds with friends and overcoming powerful foes to prove his worth.

products.title: Sakamoto Days
products.author: Yuto Suzuki
products.description: Sakamoto Days centers around Taro Sakamoto, a former hitman known for his strength and deadly skills. Now retired and running a convenience store, Sakamoto lives a peaceful life, but his past life soon catches up with him, pulling him back into the world of assassination.

products.title: Demon Slayer
products.author: Koyoharu Gotouge
products.description: Demon Slayer follows Tanjiro Kamado, a kind-hearted boy who becomes a demon slayer after his family is slaughtered by demons. With his sister Nezuko turned into a demon, Tanjiro embarks on a dangerous journey to find a cure for her and avenge his family.

products.title: Bleach
products.author: Tite Kubo
products.description: Bleach follows Ichigo Kurosaki, a teenager who gains the powers of a Soul Reaper, tasked with protecting the living world from evil spirits. As he faces terrifying enemies and uncovers dark secrets, Ichigo must balance his new responsibilities with his normal life.

products.title: One Piece
products.author: Eiichiro Oda
products.description: One Piece tells the tale of Monkey D. Luffy, a pirate with the goal of becoming the Pirate King. With his crew of unique individuals, Luffy searches for the ultimate treasure, the One Piece, while navigating dangerous seas, battling powerful foes, and discovering the mysteries of the world.

products.title: Dragon Ball Super
products.author: Akira Toriyama
products.description: Dragon Ball Super follows Goku and his friends as they defend Earth from powerful foes. The series continues the legacy of Dragon Ball Z, with Goku unlocking new powers, facing the Gods of Destruction, and participating in inter-universal tournaments, all while battling for the survival of the universe.
